The 1895–96 &lt;a href="Scottish%20Cup"&gt;Scottish Cup&lt;/a&gt; was the 23rd season of Scotland's most prestigious &lt;a href="football%20%28soccer%29"&gt;football&lt;/a&gt; knockout competition. The Cup was won by &lt;a href="Heart%20of%20Midlothian%20F.C."&gt;Heart of Midlothian&lt;/a&gt; when they beat &lt;a href="Hibernian%20F.C."&gt;Hibernian&lt;/a&gt; 3-1 in the final.
